## RLS-Standard-Patterns

**User-Scope:**
```sql
CREATE POLICY "tab_own" ON tab FOR ALL USING (user_id = auth.uid());
```

**Team-Scope (Multi-Tenant):**
```sql
CREATE POLICY "tab_team" ON tab FOR ALL USING (
  team_id IN (SELECT team_id FROM team_members WHERE user_id = auth.uid())
);
GRANT SELECT ON team_members TO authenticated;  -- Pflicht auf Hetzner!
```

**Via Parent-Join:**
```sql
CREATE POLICY "kind_team" ON kind FOR ALL USING (
  EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM pm_projects p
          WHERE p.id = project_id
            AND p.team_id IN (SELECT team_id FROM team_members WHERE user_id = auth.uid()))
);
```

**Shared-Flag:**
```sql
CREATE POLICY "kb_own_or_shared" ON knowledge_base FOR SELECT USING (
  user_id = auth.uid()
  OR (is_shared = true AND team_id IN (SELECT team_id FROM team_members WHERE user_id = auth.uid()))
);
```

